headline: Moderna (MRNA) Valuation Check After Raised 2025 Outlook And Cost Cuts At JPMorgan Conference
summary: Moderna (MRNA) has jumped back into focus after its JPMorgan Healthcare Conference update, where management lifted the 2025 revenue forecast to about US$1.9b, cut operating expense guidance by US$200m, and pointed to a stronger cash position. See our latest analysis for Moderna. The 21.95% 7 day share price return and 53.56% 90 day share price return suggest momentum has picked up recently.
